text: Langquaid is a municipality in Kelheim in Bavaria in Germany. ==Ortsteile== Villages associated to the administration (Ortsteil) of Langquaid are *Adlhausen *Hellring *Leitenhausen *Niederleierndorf *Oberleierndorf *Paring *Unterschneidhart *Mitterschneidhart *Oberschneidhart ==References== *Markt Langquaid - Ortsteile ==Other websites== *Official homepage of Markt Langquaid Category:Kelheim (district)
